    astrological: 'The Quran connects to Neptune in its highest expression — divine truth transmitted without distortion through a perfectly surrendered vessel. The 9th House of revelation and the 12th House of divine communion provide the channels. Jupiter\'s expansive wisdom and Mercury\'s linguistic precision both serve the transmission.',
