    psychological: 'Ascension symbolizes the ego\'s expansion toward the Self — the upward movement of consciousness from the personal to the transpersonal, from identification with the small self to recognition of the greater Self. The ascension dream marks a moment of psychological elevation that permanently changes your vantage point.',
