    astrological: 'Ascension connects to the Midheaven (MC) — the highest point of the chart, representing the pinnacle of worldly and spiritual achievement. Jupiter\'s expansive upward movement and Uranus\'s liberation from gravitational identity both fuel ascension. The 10th House of culmination and the 9th House of transcendence converge at the peak.',
