    astrological: 'Yantras connect to the fixed signs (Taurus, Leo, Scorpio, Aquarius) and their capacity for sustained, concentrated focus. Mars provides the sharp energy of the yantra\'s triangles, while Saturn provides the structural precision. The 8th House of concentrated power and the 5th House of creative invocation both participate.',
