    shadow: 'A microphone that fails, that produces feedback, or that amplifies the wrong message warns of miscommunication, the distortion of your message by the medium, or the terrifying discovery that what you thought was private has been broadcast publicly. The shadow microphone reveals where your voice has been silenced or distorted.',
