    psychological: 'The trench symbolizes the defensive posture of a psyche under prolonged stress — the mental state of hunkering down, minimizing exposure, and simply surviving until conditions change. The trench dream reflects chronic stress, combat fatigue, or the exhausting reality of maintaining position in a hostile environment.',
