    astrological: 'Trenches connect to Saturn in the 6th House — the experience of duty, endurance, and the grinding daily reality of maintaining a position under pressure. Capricorn\'s grim persistence and Cancer\'s defensive withdrawal both contribute to the trench mentality. Mars provides the capacity to endure; the Moon provides the emotional toll.',
    shadow: 'A trench that fills with water or that you can never leave warns of being trapped in a defensive position that has become permanent — chronic stress, learned helplessness, or the inability to transition from survival mode to living. The shadow trench reveals where you are surviving when you could be advancing.',
